<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5356891>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Schematic drawings of the internal morphology in dorsal view. A, Pheretima aquila, new species; B, P. gamay, new species; C, P. libradoi, new species; D, P. davaoensis, new species. Abbreviations: s, spermatheca; h, heart; p, prostate gland; cb, copulatory bursa; c, caecum. Scale bars = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5356891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

